ELSEIF TEQUIP:34 == 2
	TEQUIP:34 = 1
	PRINTFORML %CALLNAME:TARGET%的强精神药的效果好像中断了
	PRINTL ＜强精神药抵抗中＞
ELSEIF TEQUIP:34 == 1
	PRINTL ＜强精神药抵抗中＞
ENDIF


RETURN 1

